        <div class="group-heading">Filter by Offense:</div>
        <div class="tat-shade"><a id="filter_toggle_contact" class="filter-item" href="#">Contact</a><div class="filter-count" id="filter_count_contact"></div></div>
        <div class="bit-shade"><a id="filter_toggle_gap" class="filter-item" href="#">Gap</a><div class="filter-count" id="filter_count_gap"></div></div>
        <div class="tat-shade"><a id="filter_toggle_power" class="filter-item" href="#">Power</a><div class="filter-count" id="filter_count_power"></div></div>
        <div class="bit-shade"><a id="filter_toggle_eye" class="filter-item" href="#">Eye</a><div class="filter-count" id="filter_count_eye"></div></div>
        <div class="tat-shade"><a id="filter_toggle_avoid_k" class="filter-item" href="#">Avoid K</a><div class="filter-count" id="filter_count_avoid_k"></div></div>
        <div class="bit-shade"><a id="filter_toggle_running" class="filter-item" href="#">Running</a><div class="filter-count" id="filter_count_running"></div></div>
        <div class="tat-shade"><a id="filter_toggle_bunting" class="filter-item" href="#">Bunting</a><div class="filter-count" id="filter_count_bunting"></div></div>
        <div class="group-heading">Filter by Defense:</div>
        <div class="tat-shade"><a id="filter_toggle_infield" class="filter-item" href="#">Infield</a><div class="filter-count" id="filter_count_infield"></div></div>
        <div class="bit-shade"><a id="filter_toggle_outfield" class="filter-item" href="#">Outfield</a><div class="filter-count" id="filter_count_outfield"></div></div>
        <div class="tat-shade"><a id="filter_toggle_catcher" class="filter-item" href="#">Catcher</a><div class="filter-count" id="filter_count_catcher"></div></div>


      </nav>
      <div id="filter_area" class="column is-half">
        <section id="filter_new">
          <heading>Welcome to Perfect Scout</heading>
          <article>
            <h4>FILTER</h4>
            <p>Use Filter option(s) on the left to indicate specific kinds of players you wish to
            search for.  You can use a single filter, or as many filters as you wish.</p>
            <h4>SEARCH</h4>
            <p>After you are satisfied with your selections, click the Search Now button and Perfect
              Scout will display a list of players according to your filters.</p>
            <h4>VIEW AND COMPARE</h4>
            <p>Click on a player you would like to see more detail on.  You will also be able to
            compare the selected players to other ones next to him on the list.</p>

          </article>
        </section>
        <section id="filter_name" style="display: none;">
          <heading>Filter by Player First and Last Name</heading>
          <article>
            <div class="fieldy">
              <label for="batter_player_first_name">First Name:</label>
              <div class="control">
                <input id="batter_player_first_name" class="input name-input" type="text"
                onchange="filterCountUpdate('text', 'batter_player_first_name', 'name', this.value);" placeholder="Player First Name">
              </div>
            </div>

            <div class="fieldy">
              <label for="batter_player_last_name">Last Name:</label>
              <div class="control">
                <input size="40" id="batter_player_last_name" class="input name-input" type="text"
                onchange="filterCountUpdate('text', 'batter_player_last_name', 'name', this.value);" placeholder="Player Last Name">
              </div>
            </div>

          </article>
          <br />
          <h6>TIP: Name search is NOT case-sensitive. </h6>
          <h6>TIP: You can enter just the beginning letter(s) for first and last name searches ...
            for example, you could just enter `yas` to attempt to search for `Yastrzemski`.</h6>

        </section>

        <section id="filter_team" style="display: none;">
          <heading>Filter by Team Names</heading>
          <article>

            <div class="columns">
              <div class="column is-half">
                <div class="fieldy">
                  <label for="batter_player_team_current">Current MLB Teams:</label>
                  <div class="control">
                    <div class="select is-small is-multiple" size="8">
                      <select size="10" multiple class="team-input" id="batter_player_team_current"
                        onchange="filterCountUpdate('multiselect', 'batter_player_team_current',
                        'team', this.value);">
                          {{#each teamNamesForFilter}}
                          <option value="{{this.id}}">{{this.name}}</option>
                          {{/each}}
                      </select>
                    </div>
                    <br /><br /><a href="javascript:clearSelections('batter_player_team_current', 'team')" class="team-input button is-small">(Clear above selections)</a>
                  </div>
                </div>
              </div>
              <div class="column is-half">
                <div class="fieldy">
                  <label for="batter_player_team_historical">Historical MLB Teams:</label>
                  <div class="control">
                    <div class="select is-primary is-small is-multiple" >
                      <select size="10" multiple class="team-input" id="batter_player_team_historical"
                        onchange="filterCountUpdate('multiselect', 'batter_player_team_historical',
                        'team', this.value);">
                        {{#each historicalTeamNamesForFilter}}
                        <option value="{{this.id}}">{{this.name}}</option>
                        {{/each}}
                      </select>
                    </div>
                    <br /><br /><a href="javascript:clearSelections('batter_player_team_historical', 'team')" class="team-input button is-small">(Clear above selections)</a>
                  </div>
                </div>
              </div>
            </div>
          </article>
          <br />
          <h6>TIP: Select as many teams as you like from either or both of these lists.
          Players will match this filter if they played for ANY of the teams selected.</h6>

        </section>

        <section id="filter_position" style="display: none;">
          <heading>Filter by Listed Position</heading>
          <article>
          <div style="z-index: 1; position: absolute; top: 330px; left: 474px;">
