          </div>
          <div style="z-index: 1; position: absolute; top: 330px; left: 574px;">
            <a id="pos_1b" class="pos-sel" href="javascript:toggleDiamondPosition('1B');">1B</a>
          </div>
          <div style="z-index: 1; position: absolute; top: 414px; left: 529px;">
            <a id="pos_c" class="pos-sel" href="javascript:toggleDiamondPosition('C');">C</a>
          </div>
          <div style="z-index: 1; position: absolute; top: 304px; left: 496px;">
            <a id="pos_ss" class="pos-sel" href="javascript:toggleDiamondPosition('SS');">SS</a>
          </div>
          <div style="z-index: 1; position: absolute; top: 304px; left: 552px;">
            <a id="pos_2b" class="pos-sel" href="javascript:toggleDiamondPosition('2B');">2B</a>
          </div>
          <div style="z-index: 1; position: absolute; top: 258px; left: 450px;">
            <a id="pos_lf" class="pos-sel" href="javascript:toggleDiamondPosition('LF');">LF</a>
          </div>
          <div style="z-index: 1; position: absolute; top: 218px; left: 522px;">
            <a id="pos_cf" class="pos-sel" href="javascript:toggleDiamondPosition('CF');">CF</a>
          </div>
          <div style="z-index: 1; position: absolute; top: 258px; left: 602px;">
            <a id="pos_rf" class="pos-sel" href="javascript:toggleDiamondPosition('RF');">RF</a>
          </div>

          <svg class="bb-diamond" style="position: absolute; top: 210px; left: 340px;">
        		<line x1="50" y1="50" x2="200" y2="200" />
        		<line x1="200" y1="200" x2="350" y2="50" />
        		<line x1="150" y1="150" x2="200" y2="100" />
        		<line x1="200" y1="100" x2="250" y2="150" />

        		<polygon points="200 200, 206 194, 200 188, 194 194" />
        		<polygon points="200 100, 206 106, 200 112, 194 106" />
        		<polygon points="150 150, 156 144, 162 150, 156 156" />
        		<polygon points="250 150, 244 144, 238 150, 244 156" />
      	   </svg>

           <h6 style="margin-top: 330px; margin-left: 38px;">TIP: Select as many player positions as you like from the graphic above.</h6>
          </article>


        </section>

        <section id="filter_hand" style="display: none;">
          <heading>Filter by Batting and/or Throwing Hand</heading>
          <article>
            <div class="fieldy">
              <label for="batter_player_batting_hands">Batting Hand:</label>
              <div class="control">
                <div id="batter_player_batting_hands">
                  <span class="hand_icons"><a href="javascript:toggleBattingHand('left');"><i id="batter_player_batting_hand_left" class="lefty far fa-hand-paper"></i></a></span> Left
                  &nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp; Right
                  <span class="hand_icons"><a href="javascript:toggleBattingHand('right');"><i id="batter_player_batting_hand_right" class="far fa-hand-paper"></i></a></span>
                  &nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp; Switch
                  <span class="hand_icons"><a href="javascript:toggleBattingHand('bswitch');"><i id="batter_player_batting_hand_bswitch" class="far fa-hand-paper"></i></a></span>
              </div>
            </div>
          </div>
            <div class="fieldy">
              <label for="batter_player_throwing_hands">Throwing Hand:</label>
              <div class="control">
                <div id="batter_player_throwing_hands">
                  <span class="hand_icons"><a href="javascript:toggleThrowingHand('left');"><i id="batter_player_throwing_hand_left" class="lefty far fa-hand-paper"></i></a></span> Left
                  &nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp; Right
                  <span class="hand_icons"><a href="javascript:toggleThrowingHand('right');"><i id="batter_player_throwing_hand_right" class="far fa-hand-paper"></i></a></span>
              </div>
            </div>
          </div>
          <br />
           <h6>TIP: Use controls above if you would like to filter by batting hand and/or throwing hand.</h6>
           <h6>TIP: Only one of each group can be selected at a time.  Click the solid hand a second time to de-select.</h6>
          </article>


        </section>

        <section id="filter_ovr" style="display: none;">
          <heading>Filter by Card Overall</heading>
          <article>

            <div class="columns">
              <div class="column is-three-quarters">

                <div class="fieldy">
                  <div class="control">
                    <label for="batter_card_ovr_min">Card Overall (minimum):</label>&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;<span class="ps-slider-label" id="batter_card_ovr_min_output">70</span>
                    <br />40 <input oninput="rangeChange(this, 'ovr');" class="ps-slider" id="batter_card_ovr_min" step="1" min="40" max="100" value="70" type="range" /> 100
                  </div>
                </div>
              </div>
              <div class="column is-one-quarter">

                <div class="fieldy"><br />
                  <input onchange="rangeChangeUse(this, 'batter_card_ovr_min', 'ovr');" id="batter_card_ovr_min_on" type="checkbox" name="switchExample" class="switch">
                  <label for="batter_card_ovr_min_on">Use</label>
                </div>
              </div>
            </div>

            <div class="columns">
              <div class="column is-three-quarters">

                <div class="fieldy">
                  <div class="control">
                    <label for="batter_card_ovr_max">Card Overall (maximum):</label>&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;<span class="ps-slider-label" id="batter_card_ovr_max_output">70</span>
                    <br />40 <input oninput="rangeChange(this, 'ovr');" class="ps-slider" id="batter_card_ovr_max" step="1" min="40" max="100" value="70" type="range" /> 100
                  </div>
                </div>
              </div>
              <div class="column is-one-quarter">

                <div class="fieldy"><br />
                  <input oninput="rangeChangeUse(this, 'batter_card_ovr_max', 'ovr');" id="batter_card_ovr_max_on" type="checkbox" name="switchExample" class="switch">
                  <label for="batter_card_ovr_max_on">Use</label>
                </div>
              </div>
            </div>


          <br />
           <h6>TIP: Use the slider above to set the desired value.  If you want to turn on/off the slider for filtering,
           click the Use switch.</h6>
           <h6>TIP: If you set the maximum less than or equal to the minimum, the maximum will be disregarded.</h6>
          </article>


        </section>


        <section id="filter_card_tier" style="display: none;">
          <heading>Filter by Card Tier</heading>
          <article>

            <div class="columns card-tier-columns">
              <div class="column is-one-third">

                <div class="card-tier-hl" id="batter_card_tier_p" onclick="toggleCardTier('p');">
                  <div class="card-tier-ext tier-p">
                    <div class="card-tier-int tier-p">
                      Perfect<br />
                      (100 OVR)
                    </div>
                  </div>
                </div>
                <br />
                <div class="card-tier-hl" id="batter_card_tier_s" onclick="toggleCardTier('s');">
                  <div class="card-tier-ext tier-s">
                    <div class="card-tier-int tier-s">
                      Silver<br />
                      (70-79 OVR)
                    </div>
                  </div>
                </div>

              </div>

              <div class="column is-one-third">

              <div class="card-tier-hl" id="batter_card_tier_d" onclick="toggleCardTier('d');">
                <div class="card-tier-ext tier-d">
                  <div class="card-tier-int tier-d">
                    Diamond<br />
                    (90-99 OVR)
                  </div>
                </div>
              </div>
              <br />
              <div class="card-tier-hl" id="batter_card_tier_b" onclick="toggleCardTier('b');">
                <div class="card-tier-ext tier-b">
                  <div class="card-tier-int tier-b">
                    Bronze<br />
                    (60-69 OVR)
                  </div>
                </div>
              </div>

            </div>

            <div class="column is-one-third">

            <div class="card-tier-hl" id="batter_card_tier_g" onclick="toggleCardTier('g');">
              <div class="card-tier-ext tier-g">
                <div class="card-tier-int tier-g">
                  Gold<br />
                  (80-89 OVR)
                </div>
              </div>
            </div>
            <br />
            <div class="card-tier-hl" id="batter_card_tier_i" onclick="toggleCardTier('i');">
              <div class="card-tier-ext tier-i">
                <div class="card-tier-int tier-i">
                  Iron<br />
                  (40-59 OVR)
                </div>
              </div>
            </div>

          </div>

            </div> <!-- end columns -->
           <h6>TIP: Select and de-select one or more card tier(s) above to filter.</h6>
          </article>


        </section>

        <section id="filter_card_type" style="display: none;">
          <heading>Filter by Card Types</heading>
          <article>


                <div class="fieldy">
                  <label for="batter_card_type_program">Card Types:</label>
                  <div class="control">
                    <div class="select is-small is-multiple" size="8">
                      <select size="8" multiple class="team-input" id="batter_card_type_program"
                        onchange="filterCountUpdate('multiselect', 'batter_card_type_program',
                        'card_type', this.value);">
                          {{#each cardTypesProgramsForFilter}}
                            <option value="{{this.abbrev}}">{{this.name}}</option>
                          {{/each}}
                      </select>
                    </div>
                    <br /><br /><a href="javascript:clearSelections('batter_card_type_program', 'card_type')" class="team-input button is-small">(Clear above selections)</a>
                  </div>
                </div>
          </article>
          <br />
          <h6>TIP: Select as many card types as you like from the list above.
          Players will match this filter if they are ANY of the card types selected.</h6>

        </section>

                <section id="filter_card_year" style="display: none;">
                  <heading>Filter by Card Year</heading>
                  <article>

                    <div class="columns">
                      <div class="column is-three-quarters">

                        <div class="fieldy">
                          <div class="control">
                            <label for="batter_card_year_min">Card Year (minimum):</label>&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;<span class="ps-slider-label" id="batter_card_year_min_output">1954</span>
                            <br />1886 <input oninput="rangeChange(this, 'card_year');" class="ps-slider year" id="batter_card_year_min" step="1" min="1886" max="2019" value="1954" type="range" /> 2019
                          </div>
                        </div>
                      </div>
                      <div class="column is-one-quarter">

                        <div class="fieldy"><br />
                          <input oninput="rangeChangeUse(this, 'batter_card_year_min', 'card_year');" id="batter_card_year_min_on" type="checkbox" name="switchExample" class="switch">
                          <label for="batter_card_year_min_on">Use</label>
                        </div>
                      </div>
                    </div>

                    <div class="columns">
                      <div class="column is-three-quarters">

                        <div class="fieldy">
                          <div class="control">
                            <label for="batter_card_year_max">Card Year (maximum):</label>&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;<span class="ps-slider-label" id="batter_card_year_max_output">1954</span>
                            <br />1886 <input oninput="rangeChange(this, 'card_year');" class="ps-slider year" id="batter_card_year_max" step="1" min="1886" max="2019" value="1954" type="range" /> 2019
                          </div>
                        </div>
                      </div>
                      <div class="column is-one-quarter">

                        <div class="fieldy"><br />
                          <input oninput="rangeChangeUse(this, 'batter_card_year_max', 'card_year');" id="batter_card_year_max_on" type="checkbox" name="switchExample" class="switch">
                          <label for="batter_card_year_max_on">Use</label>
                        </div>
                      </div>
                    </div>


                  <br />
                   <h6>TIP: Use the slider above to set the desired value.  If you want to turn on/off the slider for filtering,
                   click the Use switch.</h6>
                   <h6>TIP: If you set the maximum less than or equal to the minimum, the maximum will be disregarded.</h6>
                  </article>


                </section>

      </div>
    <aside class="search-result-panel column is-one-quarter">
      <a class="button">Search Now</a>
      <br />
      <h4>Note:</h4>
      <p>Your search results will be limited to the top 50 players to keep the number of players
        you wish to compare to manageable.  If you aren't satisfied with the players returned,
        consider using additional filters.</p>
    </aside>
  </div>
